{"tid":551780,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「所有野都係整定」其實唔係迷信係科學","createTime":"2018-02-06T03:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T18:13:19.000Z","uid":114633,"like":37,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2156504e62334e13bf045009726784a0bb3fc7","tid":551780,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Everything has a cause.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n我哋覺得自己有自由意志 <br />\n但其實只係一個假象 <br />\n因為所有野係宇宙大爆炸嗰刻已經決定咗<br />\n<br />\n世界萬物嘅發生都係因為有原因先會有結果<br />\n當你搵唔到份好工 <br />\n可能係因為你入唔倒好嘅大學<br />\n入唔到好嘅大學<br />\n可能因為你父母財政或者學歷低<br />\n而你父母學歷低<br />\n可能係因為你公公婆婆嗰個年代生活差 <br />\n搞到佢無機會讀書 <br />\n<br />\n即係如果你今日個結果係唔搵到份好工<br />\n其實個原因係你未出世既時候已經決定左<br />\n你以為自己有得揀 <br />\n但其實你根本改變唔倒"},{"pid":"ee520a617e46ebbf1ef3fab89d5afe9cde6dc9e3","tid":551780,"uid":3441,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"6c2156504e62334e13bf045009726784a0bb3fc7","tid":551780,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Everything has a cause.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n我哋覺得自己有自由意志 <br />\n但其實只係一個假象 <br />\n因為所有野係宇宙大爆炸嗰刻已經決定咗<br />\n<br />\n世界萬物嘅發生都係因為有原因先會有結果<br />\n當你搵唔到份好工 <br />\n可能係因為你入唔倒好嘅大學<br />\n入唔到好嘅大學<br />\n可能因為你父母財政或者學歷低<br />\n而你父母學歷低<br />\n可能係因為你公公婆婆嗰個年代生活差 <br />\n搞到佢無機會讀書 <br />\n<br />\n即係如果你今日個結果係唔搵到份好工<br />\n其實個原因係你未出世既時候已經決定左<br />\n你以為自己有得揀 <br />\n但其實你根本改變唔倒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"你個claim點驗證，是否falsifiable? 如果唔得就算唔上科學。"},{"pid":"7338a2f001602b5b56944ff578bd92b8af79810c","tid":551780,"uid":80015,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺人類根本冇 free will ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/420716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/420716/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7a99b5467d52a2de646092a95ff859895452cb12","tid":551780,"uid":33808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"我成日都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過人而家無辦法完全意識到呢個事實<br />\n因為人對萬物嘅因果了解有限<br />\n而且知咗對現實冇幫助<br />\n所以寧願相信有人定勝天<br />\n根本世界就好似一堆桌球咁<br />\n一野撞開嗰陣四散亂飛<br />\n但無論幾亂，軌跡其實一早定曬<br />\n依然係你唔做就唔會有相應成就<br />\n不過固定咗嘅係你會唔會做咁解<br />\n而相應地都有固定咗嘅前因同後果"},{"pid":"73dba2e2e3dc282a7d0d65f8979f31fe74323fec","tid":551780,"uid":2364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a99b5467d52a2de646092a95ff859895452cb12","tid":551780,"uid":33808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"我成日都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過人而家無辦法完全意識到呢個事實<br />\n因為人對萬物嘅因果了解有限<br />\n而且知咗對現實冇幫助<br />\n所以寧願相信有人定勝天<br />\n根本世界就好似一堆桌球咁<br />\n一野撞開嗰陣四散亂飛<br />\n但無論幾亂，軌跡其實一早定曬<br />\n依然係你唔做就唔會有相應成就<br />\n不過固定咗嘅係你會唔會做咁解<br />\n而相應地都有固定咗嘅前因同後果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"你又知係事實？"},{"pid":"d30c584c2c7e16db4e38fdd3f9f1e03403db6a61","tid":551780,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"當偶然無到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},{"pid":"cd1b62870e7f3e35db1b1cf9a8704ae24c378898","tid":551780,"uid":114633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4e53b412961014781c24a49cac70ac5d2ef6ec","tid":551780,"uid":70760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"近年腦神經科學好似證到大腦做決定前0.0幾秒之前已有決定, 即係人無自由意志<br />\n<br />\n定還是自由意志個定義係呢到可以討論? (因為哲學上都好似有分soft同hard )<br />\n<br />\n唔是好識,講錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737a64d2561acfb50d336e4f9980e8f96cac251e","tid":551780,"uid":36158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"cbd0a1ea28e8d3692aaf740a9d367d51201bcb98","tid":551780,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"講緊快餐店？"},{"pid":"007f12b15baab8bd4f0c42afe4cfd10ef3a2b962","tid":551780,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺唔覺人類根本冇 free will ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/420716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/420716/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n覺唔覺人類根本冇 free wifi?"},{"pid":"ee45602e8d58e7e1871945f1c7cebf94518b1c5a","tid":551780,"uid":88999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"結果論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b407d104660ad1a2264f901aca4d3b4b0ec0d1","tid":551780,"uid":156197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f4e53b412961014781c24a49cac70ac5d2ef6ec","tid":551780,"uid":70760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"近年腦神經科學好似證到大腦做決定前0.0幾秒之前已有決定, 即係人無自由意志<br />\n<br />\n定還是自由意志個定義係呢到可以討論? (因為哲學上都好似有分soft同hard )<br />\n<br />\n唔是好識,講錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:56:33.000Z","msg":"soft / hard 果個係determinism <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有philosophers話soft determinism 可以同free will 係compatible <br />\n<br />\n但有人覺得兩樣野從根本上唔可以共存 因為free will 包括左own belief + capability to change things based on that belief 嘅哩層定義 所以因為determinism令事情無改變嘅空間，free will就其實唔係free嘅<br />\n<br />\nquantum mechanics 嘅例子係講某啲outcome其實唔follow d causes 計到嘅只有probability <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得值得討論嘅係，即使我哋有啲想法係pre-determined (由我地改變唔到嘅前因而有某些想法） 但又因為哩個belief而作出相應嘅action <br />\n咁determinism 同free will 又唔可以講唔係同時存在<br />\n<br />\nphilo毒撚講嘢有點1999請見諒"},{"pid":"875a8cfe5b4a3d77f1a936305ab93ffa41a1c19c","tid":551780,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"第3組二律背反（關於自由意志） 正命題： 宇宙的各種現象，不只是由遵照自然法則運作的因果律主導的，還受到自由意志的因果律影響。反命題： 沒有自由意志這種東西，在宇宙中任何東西純粹遵照自然法則運作"},{"pid":"f39a393a23f05ccea71c7296a8124f26275400b3","tid":551780,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:17:29.000Z","msg":"建議可以查下<br />\n一般認為人如果無辦法擺脫時間 空間 因果嘅約束<br />\n自由意志有家冇 永遠都唔會知"},{"pid":"beb766cefd80036b52596b67bb09f809d61874e0","tid":551780,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:33:55.000Z","msg":"呢樣野有個topic叫決定論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5285c51f324df7cea04eac656c73f4474f5c11c","tid":551780,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:41:28.000Z","msg":"因為時間關係......<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/7/1501087056_Qr-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F7%2F1501087056_Qr-1280w.jpg&h=945bed63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d102dcbe6dfddc277d7d0c26199c043fcf01cfb0","tid":551780,"uid":45773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:46:27.000Z","msg":"量子力學從來都冇否定或者肯定決定論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然量子力學好多情況計出嚟嘅數都係機率，好似wave function咁，但原因係因為不確定性原理，人類冇方法得出所有(條件)嚟計數，所以對於決定論大部分科學家都係不可知論者"},{"pid":"dbfa0e91e796f255de757889cbb7f9695c1c88fe","tid":551780,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:47:55.000Z","msg":"fatalism"},{"pid":"499ac533662d0db73bdce070373c4a6f1128d648","tid":551780,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:50:43.000Z","msg":"人既自由意志係有局限<br />\n可改變<br />\n但唔係一時三刻<br />\n可能要大半世人既努力"},{"pid":"69e77d8cfee0cc3f63fbb08b9beb66b65bab2e8a","tid":551780,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下量子力學</blockquote>近年腦神經科學好似證到大腦做決定前0.0幾秒之前已有決定, 即係人無自由意志<br />\n<br />\n定還是自由意志個定義係呢到可以討論? (因為哲學上都好似有分soft同hard )<br />\n<br />\n唔是好識,講錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都聽過呢個講法<br />\n第一次接觸係睇一個叫brain game的電視節目<br />\n實驗係叫佢地隨時禁個制 然後記錄低決定的時間 同埋禁個制的時間<br />\n結果發現佢地決定禁制之前個腦已經有跡象顯示佢地會禁制<br />\n<br />\n但我唔覺得咁就代表冇自由意志<br />\n以我所知 係佢地做決定之前的0.幾秒之前個腦有反應<br />\n但究竟腦部的反應係代表乜？<br />\n我地觀測到的只係佢地做決定之前 個腦已經有反應(可能係決定)<br />\n就算係決定之前已經有決定<br />\n咁係乜野令我地有呢個決定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實原本個實驗係點做<br />\n如果是矇住雙眼 聽到咇一聽就即刻禁制<br />\n咁我地究竟係聽到咇一聲就禁制 定係聽到咇一聲就決定禁制"},{"pid":"c0385605933d5fabef173747a2af634182e75b7f","tid":551780,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4e53b412961014781c24a49cac70ac5d2ef6ec","tid":551780,"uid":70760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"近年腦神經科學好似證到大腦做決定前0.0幾秒之前已有決定, 即係人無自由意志<br />\n<br />\n定還是自由意志個定義係呢到可以討論? (因為哲學上都好似有分soft同hard )<br />\n<br />\n唔是好識,講錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:20:19.000Z","msg":"霍金天才教室有集有實驗係依個<br />\n好似話類似係潛意識簡左，唔係你個意識簡，所以假設人係冇自由意志"},{"pid":"6712096c8c392f4c1788702b37818f3b1a9911f0","tid":551780,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:23:59.000Z","msg":"撚唔知咩，實係最好啦做李+x 個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2167d62d1e241d96879a05115b5a6a145b09f896","tid":551780,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0385605933d5fabef173747a2af634182e75b7f","tid":551780,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4e53b412961014781c24a49cac70ac5d2ef6ec","tid":551780,"uid":70760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"469c6068bb4426311d48704fd608e35121b0f88e","tid":551780,"uid":26030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇下量子力學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"近年腦神經科學好似證到大腦做決定前0.0幾秒之前已有決定, 即係人無自由意志<br />\n<br />\n定還是自由意志個定義係呢到可以討論? (因為哲學上都好似有分soft同hard )<br />\n<br />\n唔是好識,講錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T22:20:19.000Z","msg":"霍金天才教室有集有實驗係依個<br />\n好似話類似係潛意識簡左，唔係你個意識簡，所以假設人係冇自由意志"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"潛意識唔屬於意志嘅一部分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果自由意志嘅特質係人嘅信念及選擇<br />\n而human mind係包含意識同潛意識<br />\n咁點解建基於潛意識嘅選擇就唔被視為&quot;自由&quot;?<br />\n人潛意識嘅信念不能被稱為人嘅信念？<br />\n難道潛意識不屬於個人嘅一部分？<br />\n<br />\n雖然潛意識嘅建立係多受成長環境影響<br />\n而其運作又不受意識控制<br />\n但係都唔足以證明&quot;人冇自由意志&quot;呢個結論<br />\n即使結合各種心理學或精神分析理論<br />\n最多只能夠推論&quot;意識係不自由&quot;或&quot;潛意識控制個人較意識多&quot;等結論<br />\n但呢啲結論並冇否定潛意識可以擁有自由<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}